			<CASNumber>007719-12-2</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Phosphorus trichloride is an inorganic compound with the chemical formula PCl 3. It is a colorless liquid when pure and is an important industrial chemical. It is used for the manufacture of phosphites and other organophosphorus compounds. It is toxic and reacts readily with water to release hydrogen chloride. It is a strong oxidizer and will readily react with many organic compounds. It is used to make a variety of compounds including pesticides and flame retardants.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">三氯化磷是一种无机化合物，化学式为 PCl 3。纯品为无色液体，是一种重要的工业化学品。它用于制造亚磷酸盐和其他有机磷化合物。它有毒，容易与水反应，释放出氯化氢。它是一种强氧化剂，很容易与许多有机化合物发生反应。它可用于制造各种化合物，包括杀虫剂和阻燃剂。</common:generalComment>
